		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (30184,509,'You recognize the landscape as being Dunwich, but you see no recognizable buildings. A group of Vikings stand near a large stone covered in glyphs and are speaking a language you don''t understand. When the discussion is over, they begin to bury the stone. Make a <b>Will (-1) check</b> to memorize the location. If you pass, gain 2 Clue tokens.')");
