		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1429,39,'An unshaven, down-on-his-luck painter sits on the street corner, selling some of his possessions to make ends meet. Draw 1 Common Item. You may buy it for $2, regardless of its list price. If you don''t buy the item, discard it.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (428,1430)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1430,41,'You stumble across an excerpt from the Necronomicon in the archives. Pass a <b>Lore (-1) [2] check</b> to search the Spell deck and take a spell of your choice.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (428,1431)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1431,42,'Neil rambles on as he gives you the guided tour. It''s entertaining, but ultimately useless. Nothing happens.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (429,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (429,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (429,1432)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1432,39,'As you stroll past a pale, dark haired woman, she mumbles to herself, \"Charles, I''m sorry. It was all my fault.\" Concerned, you take a second look at her and see a young woman consumed with guilt and grief. If you talk to her, make a <b>Will (-2) check</b>. If you pass, you find out that her name is Corla Fistienne and her ex-boyfriend recently committed suicide. You leave feeling that you''ve helped alleviate her guilt and prevented her from doing anything stupid. Gain 2 Sanity. If you fail or do not try to talk to her, the terror level increases by 1 when news of her suicide reaches the newspapers the next day.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (429,1433)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1433,41,'The halls are too crowded with students to proceed. Move to the street.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (429,1434)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1434,42,'Neil buys a worthless, but odd-looking trinket from you. Gain $1.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (430,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (430,10)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (430,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (430,1435)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1435,39,'As you walk down the street, a tomcat rubs himself across your legs. \"Hello there, puss. Where did you come from?\" If you pass a <b>Luck (-1) check</b>, you name the cat <b>Foolishness</b>. Take his Ally card, or if it''s not available, remove 2 rift tokens from the Kingsport board.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (430,1436)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1436,41,'One of the classrooms is closed today and students are not allowed to go in. Inside you find animal blood was painted on the walls as part of some horrific rite. Lose 1 Sanity.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (430,1437)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1437,42,'You realize that an old book that Neil has just received has been serving as a nest for a multitude of biting insects. Make a <b>Speed (-2) check</b> to get it outside before they start spreading. If you fail, lose 1 Stamina.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (431,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (431,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (431,1438)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1438,39,'As you walk down the street, a tomcat rubs himself across your legs. \"Hello there, puss. Where did you come from?\" If you pass a <b>Luck (-1) check</b>, you name the cat <b>Foolishness</b>. Take his Ally card, or if it''s not available, remove 2 rift tokens from the Kingsport board.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (431,1439)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1439,41,'You have a long talk with Principal Miles. Pass a <b>Will (-1) check</b> to gain 1 Clue token, otherwise move to the street.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (431,1440)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1440,42,'\"I guarantee you''ve never seen anything like this!\" Neil holds up a jar containing a small white creature. You may pay $1 to examine it and make a <b>Lore (-1) check</b>. If you pass, gain 2 Clue tokens. If you fail, you gain 1 brood token if Eihort is the Ancient One. Otherwise, nothing happens.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (432,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (432,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (432,1441)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1441,39,'As you walk down the street, a tomcat rubs himself across your legs. \"Hello there, puss. Where did you come from?\" If you pass a <b>Luck (-1) check</b>, you name the cat <b>Foolishness</b>. Take his Ally card or, if it''s not available, remove 2 rift tokens from the Kingsport board.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (432,1442)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1442,41,'Principal Miles is suspicious of your presence at his school. Pass a <b>Will (-2) check</b> or be <i>arrested</i> and go to the Police Station.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (432,1443)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1443,42,'Neil shows you a grey, warty thing in a jar. As you stare, it slowly opens it eyes and meets your gaze. You may pay $1 to pass a <b>Lore (-1) [2] check</b>. If you pass, you gain 2 Clue tokens and draw 3 Spells, keeping 1 of them. If you don''t pay or fail the check, nothing happens.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (433,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (433,10)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (433,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (433,1444)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1444,39,'As you walk down the street, a tomcat rubs himself across your legs. \"Hello there, puss. Where did you come from?\" If you pass a <b>Luck (-1) check</b>, you name the cat <b>Foolishness</b>. Take his Ally card or, if it''s not available, remove 2 rift tokens from the Kingsport board.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (433,1445)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1445,41,'The students seem all too eager to tell you rumors and ghost stories. Make a <b>Lore (-1) check</b> to discern the useful from the hyperbole. If you pass, gain 1 Clue token. If you fail, you are <i>delayed</i> by the excess of dubious information.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (433,1446)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1446,42,'\"I''m running out of room, I''m afraid.\" Neil is willing to sell some of his inventory for a discount. Draw 1 Unique Item. You may purchase it for $2 less than the list price, to a minimum of $1.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (434,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (434,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (434,1447)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1447,39,'At a small corner bar, you run into Derek Minot, who is busily getting drunk. Seeing a sympathetic ear, he tells you the tragic tale of his roommate, who recently killed himself. The tale is unpleasant and peculiar, making you suspect unnatural influences at work. Pass a <b>Will (-2) check</b> or lose 1 Sanity and 1 Stamina. In any event, gain 1 Clue token.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (434,1448)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1448,41,'Having gotten permission to look through the archive in the basement, you come across a parchment signed by Eben Hall. Pass a <b>Lore (-1) check</b> to gain 1 Spell.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (434,1449)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1449,42,'Neil shows you his collection of  primitive items. Something among them catches your eye. Draw 1 Unique Item. You may buy it for its list price plus $1.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (435,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (435,10)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (435,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (435,9)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (435,1450)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1450,39,'<b>Erica Carlyle</b> is browsing the art for sale and gets caught up in your stories of the unexplained. If you have $3 or less, she agrees to join you and help pay your way. Take her Ally card or, if it is not available, gain a Retainer card.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (435,1451)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1451,41,'After looking in the school records, you begin to feel a malevolent force has begun to follow you. Make a <b>Will (-1) check</b> to shake the feeling. If you fail, take the Harried card if it is available.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (435,1452)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1452,42,'You are shocked to discover a genuine ancient Egyptian treasure among Neil''s trinkets. Stranger still, he seems eager for you to take it off his hands at no charge. You may gain 1 Exhibit Item if you wish. If you you, take the Tainted card if it is available.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (436,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (436,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (436,1453)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1453,39,'If you have a <i><b>Tome</b></i>, a gaunt man with a maniacal gleam in his eyes comes up to you in the street. Introducing himself as Jim Redmond, he offers to buy any one of your <i><b>Tomes</b></i> for $5. If you sell it to him, return it to the box, gain $5, and lose 1 Sanity as you worry what he''s going to do with it. If you do not sell a <i><b>Tome</b></i> to Jim, or do not have one, nothing happens.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (436,1454)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1454,41,'You read a book in the library about some horrible Polynesian rituals. Lose 1 Sanity.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (436,1455)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1455,42,'You see a strange young man dickering with Neil over the price of a musty book. \"Blast you, man! Just set a price, already!\" It turns out that Neil''s more interested in a couple of your items, however. If you discard 2 Common Items the young man gives his name as <b>Charles Dexter Ward</b>. Take his Ally card, or if it''s not available, draw the top 5 Spells and keep one of them.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (437,16)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardExp + " (437,5)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (437,1456)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1456,39,'Passing a thin, pale artist who has a nasty twitch, you glance at one of his paintings and your horrified gaze is immediately captured. Pass a <b>Will (-1) check</b> or lose 1 Sanity and become <i>delayed</i> as you faint upon seeing the nightmarish creature he has depicted.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (437,1457)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1457,41,'Underneath some papers in the archive, you see a glint of light. Pass a <b>Luck (-2) check</b> to gain 1 Unique Item.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (437,1458)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1458,42,'\"Wow! That would look great next to the Babylonian scroll cylinders!\" Neil offers to buy a Unique Item from you for $3 more than its list price.')");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCard + " (438,16)");
